### Signup
POST http://localhost:8088/api/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "Email": "safa@example.com",
  "Password": "Secure123",
  "Name": "Safa",
  "Experience": "experienced"
}

### Login
POST http://localhost:8088/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "Email": "safa@example.com",
  "Password": "Secure123"
}

### Me (needs cookies from login)
GET http://localhost:8088/api/auth/me

### Refresh — cookie values should CHANGE
POST http://localhost:8088/api/auth/refresh

### Logout
POST http://localhost:8088/api/auth/logout

### Refresh after logout — MUST be 401
POST http://localhost:8088/api/auth/refresh



### ── OUTING CEREMONY ──────────────────────────────

### 0. Signup mika (once)
POST http://localhost:8088/api/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "Email": "mika@example.com",
  "Password": "Secure123",
  "Name": "Mika",
  "Experience": "beginner"
}

### 1. Login as SAFA (host)
POST http://localhost:8088/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{ "Email": "safa@example.com", "Password": "Secure123" }

### 2. safa creates outing → 201, COPY the outing id
POST http://localhost:8088/api/outings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Rattlesnake Ledge sunrise",
  "destination": "Rattlesnake Ledge",
  "meet_label": "Upper lot, Rattlesnake Lake",
  "starts_at": "2026-07-21T06:00:00Z",
  "max_size": 3,
  "host_seats": 3,
  "cost_per_seat_cents": 0,
  "difficulty": "moderate",
  "pace": "relaxed"
}

### 3. Login as MIKA
POST http://localhost:8088/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{ "Email": "mika@example.com", "Password": "Secure123" }

### 4. mika requests join → 201, COPY the request id
POST http://localhost:8088/api/outings/f46f8f13-965b-4247-af89-302e29955cbc/requests
Content-Type: application/json

{ "role": "rider", "seats_offered": 0, "guests": 1 }

### 5. Login as SAFA
POST http://localhost:8088/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{ "Email": "safa@example.com", "Password": "Secure123" }

### 6. safa accepts → 200  (headcount 3/3 — exactly full)
POST http://localhost:8088/api/requests/78f545d6-fb93-4a00-8cca-13a229c5f79f/accept

### 7. safa accepts AGAIN → 409 not pending
POST http://localhost:8088/api/requests/REQUEST_ID_HERE/accept

### 8. Login as MIKA
POST http://localhost:8088/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{ "Email": "mika@example.com", "Password": "Secure123" }

### 9. mika withdraws → 200
DELETE http://localhost:8088/api/outings/356317fd-a413-4baf-8ea3-fbdcc9e3702e/requests/me

### 10. mika re-requests → 201  (withdrawn→requested flip!)
POST http://localhost:8088/api/outings/356317fd-a413-4baf-8ea3-fbdcc9e3702e/requests
Content-Type: application/json

{ "role": "rider", "seats_offered": 0, "guests": 1 }

### 11. mika tries to accept HIMSELF → 403 host-only
POST http://localhost:8088/api/requests/78f545d6-fb93-4a00-8cca-13a229c5f79f/accept

### 12. Login as SAFA
POST http://localhost:8088/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{ "Email": "safa@example.com", "Password": "Secure123" }

### 13. safa declines → 200
POST http://localhost:8088/api/requests/78f545d6-fb93-4a00-8cca-13a229c5f79f/decline

### 14. Login as MIKA + re-request → 409 declined is terminal
POST http://localhost:8088/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{ "Email": "mika@example.com", "Password": "Secure123" }

### 14b.
POST http://localhost:8088/api/outings/356317fd-a413-4baf-8ea3-fbdcc9e3702e/requests
Content-Type: application/json

{ "role": "rider", "seats_offered": 0, "guests": 1 }

### 15. Garbage UUID → 400
POST http://localhost:8088/api/requests/not-a-uuid/accept